name: [24/24] Secrets of Osaka - Way back home ||　家に帰る
description:
"Happy to finally returning back home. You see this family on the other side, reminding you of the time you spend with your family. It's your time now. Or maybe not yet?" 

Twentyfourth and last picture of the 24 Days NFT Photography Adv(HEN)t Series. Secrets of Osaka's Sidealleys and Streets. Showing the exact coordinates of the Location the Photo was shot. We can go home again.
